   USERFONT/S

Use the user specified font in the clock.  

@EndNode

@Node "FONT_K <fontname.font fontheight>" "Event!.guide/FONT/K <fontname.font fontheight>"
@ToC  "Clock type specification"

   FONT/K <fontname.font fontheight>

Use  the  font  specified in the clock.  May even be proportional.
You will only have visible results if USERFONT is set.  

    Example: FONT "topaz.font,9" 


@EndNode

@Node "DONTFOLLOW_S" "Event!.guide/DONTFOLLOW/S"
